 library.
http://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/utils/util-linux/

@@

Package: cal
Version: 2.21.2-1
Depends: +libc +USE_GLIBC:librt +USE_GLIBC:libpthread +libncurses
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Build-Depends: libncurses
Section: utils
Category: Utilities
Title: display a calendar
Maintainer: 
Source: util-linux-2.21.2.tar.xz
