Source-Makefile: package/utils/picocom/Makefile
Package: picocom
Submenu: Terminal
Version: 1.6-1
Depends: +libc +USE_GLIBC:librt +USE_GLIBC:libpthread 
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: utils
Category: Utilities
Title: A minimal dumb-terminal emulation program
Maintainer: 
Source: picocom-1.6.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description: 	As its name suggests, picocom is a minimal dumb-terminal emulation 
	program. It is, in principle, very much like minicom, only it's pico 
	instead of mini! It was designed to serve as a simple, manual, modem 
	configuration, testing, and debugging tool. It has also served (quite 
	well) as a low-tech "terminal-window" to allow operator intervention 
	in PPP connection scripts. It could also prove useful in many other 
	similar tasks.
http://code.google.com/p/picocom/

@@


