Package: 6distributed
Version: 2012-12-28-20784e586f7f18a791d7fc0fce20ef125e504849
Depends: +libc +USE_GLIBC:librt +USE_GLIBC:libpthread +kmod-ipv6 +libubus +libubox
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: ipv6
Category: IPv6
Title: IPv6 host prefix distribution daemon
Maintainer: Steven Barth <steven@midlink.org>
Source: 6distributed-2012-12-28.tar.bz2
Type: ipkg
Description:  6distributed is a daemon that distributes IPv6 prefixes locally across
 downstream interfaces. It supports valid and preferred lifetimes and
 delayed allocation so that an already acquired prefix can be distributed
 on interfaces that come up later.
Steven Barth <steven@midlink.org>
@@


